script/ui/menu.py:
     # make new menu
     menu(paraclass)
     # add choices
     choices['c'] = "chat"
     # update and refresh menu
     menu.update(choices)
  - a simple menu class that display's a user menu using
    a readonly paraclass and a high split value by default.
